    },
    "paragraph-4d4a3051996e": {
      "status": "translated",
      "inlines": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "对偶Q网络（"
        },
        {
          "type": "link",
          "attrs": {
            "url": "https://arxiv.org/pdf/1511.06581.pdf"
          },
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Wang 等人，2016"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "）配备了增强的网络架构：输出层分支为两个头部，一个用于预测状态值V，另一个用于"
        },
        {
          "type": "link",
          "attrs": {
            "url": "https://lilianweng.github.io/posts/2018-02-19-rl-overview/#value-function"
          },
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "优势"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "A。然后重构Q值，"
        },
        {
          "type": "inline_math",
          "text": "Q(s, a) = V(s) + A(s, a)"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    "paragraph-25b0293ec606": {
      "status": "translated",
      "inlines": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "为确保估计的优势值总和为零，"
        },
        {
          "type": "inline_math",
          "text": "\\sum_a A(s, a)\\pi(a \\vert s) = 0"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "，我们从预测中减去平均值。"
        }
      ]
    },
