    "heading-60f73880d24f": {
      "status": "translated",
      "inlines": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "蒙特卡洛策略梯度"
        }
      ]
    },
    "paragraph-bc3f50132a66": {
      "status": "translated",
      "inlines": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "我在"
        },
        {
          "type": "link",
          "attrs": {
            "url": "https://lilianweng.github.io/posts/2018-04-08-policy-gradient/"
          },
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "上一篇文章"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "中回顾了一些流行的策略梯度方法。蒙特卡洛策略梯度，也称为"
        },
        {
          "type": "link",
          "attrs": {
            "url": "https://lilianweng.github.io/posts/2018-04-08-policy-gradient/#reinforce"
          },
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "REINFORCE"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "，是一种经典的在策略方法，它明确地学习策略模型。它使用从完整的在策略轨迹中估计的收益，并用策略梯度更新策略参数。"
        }
      ]
    },
    "paragraph-67e6e8090384": {
      "status": "translated",
      "inlines": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "收益在rollout期间计算，然后作为输入馈送到Tensorflow图中。"
        }
      ]
    },
    "paragraph-cf66eddb12e7": {
      "status": "translated",
      "inlines": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "策略网络已构建。我们通过最小化损失函数 "
        },
        {
          "type": "inline_math",
          "text": "\\mathcal{L} = - (G_t - V(s)) \\log \\pi(a \\vert s)"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " 来更新策略参数。\n"
        },
        {
          "type": "link",
          "attrs": {
            "url": "https://www.tensorflow.org/api_docs/python/tf/nn/sparse_softmax_cross_entropy_with_logits"
          },
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "tf.nn.sparse_softmax_cross_entropy_with_logits()"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " 要求将原始 logits 作为输入，而不是 softmax 后的概率，这就是为什么我们不在策略网络之上添加 softmax 层的原因。"
        }
      ]
    },
    "paragraph-bb88e82237e0": {
      "status": "translated",
      "inlines": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "在回合展开期间，回报计算如下："
        }
      ]
    },
    "paragraph-54712f905a35": {
      "status": "translated",
      "inlines": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "REINFORCE 的完整实现请见"
